body:
Korean and Egyptian activists held a protest together in front of the Egyptian Embassy in Seoul today. Several local media published articles on today's demonstration which titled '
A Protest for Mubarak's Withdrawl and Egyptian's Freedom'. The Financial News posted five photos of the protest(Click the black box below article).

title: Egypt Protests 2011 in Seoul, South Korea.
